Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就像是复活一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊 面麻居然为了让你帮她实现愿望而回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…我想应该只是我看到的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉？那是说魔幻？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 她现在也在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这吗 这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪啊 面麻 露个脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一冲动把面麻的事情说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他竟然这么轻易就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了只是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密基地是你一直在用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过仅限我待在日本的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那些红色标记 都是我去过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去世界各地看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在用打工攒的钱去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有时间去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前去了东南亚环游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越南的女孩超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明是个小不点 居然长成这么大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.52,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这样这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.44,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱啊 萌死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jungle cruise 会出现什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑题了 跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说面麻的愿望来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做过什么约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我没什么印象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是说过想要仁碳手里的「Desu Yo.」签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:42.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Desu Yo.：日本搞笑艺人 本名齐藤哲也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会为了「Desu Yo.」的签名特意化成鬼回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 栗丸你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家喂你酸奶喝啊 酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 鸣子 你真的去了宿海的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被迫去搭理一个家里蹲 真够你受的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 偶尔不都会有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知为啥提不起精神 早上爬不起来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 经常会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 但是不想被人跟那种阴暗的家伙放到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在肯定在拿鸣子你YY一些色色的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王大附高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤…鹤见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 你忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下你可以不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被谁看到我和绿高的人说话会很丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 人家好心帮你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候变得这么拽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直是怯生生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:02.25,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不要不要 别吵 安鸣和鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.56,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不许吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从以前开始就很容易受人影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和跟你一起的那些貌似胯下轻浮的女人没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胯下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前总是在模仿本间芽依子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要随便提起死人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说完自己倒憋屈 真是无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是你 还是雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要变成面麻那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 仁碳你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有那样挑动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢这种丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 也不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一呱呱 就该回家家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻…应该回去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？Nokemon？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.42,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏游戏POKEMON(PM) 以下简称NM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对客人买的东西有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一版NM 乳白？翠绿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？NM金？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少年前出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有的话就卖给我 快点卖给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀有NM？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 面麻不是很想要来着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 她一直念叨什么「Building Builder」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4,571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前的游戏还按定价 真会坑钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你 这可是良心价
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很难搞到了 所以有升值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 回来啦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天现场出了不错的盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今晚吃烤肉大餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊 一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么玩来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…首先从三只中选一只
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力具现成的我的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就应该是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:22.06,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,130)}第2话 勇者面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者面麻发现NM商店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波…久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一样还叫我波波就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么见外嘛 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被人这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 对了 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了没 面麻在仁碳那里复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 到现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 宿海怎么说面麻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 仁碳啊 好久没见他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是那么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海怎么说面麻的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听？好像是幻觉什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不太清楚 但好像是面麻想让他实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不小心睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 你回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你洗什么澡啊 老爸明明还在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 洗身子只觉得凉飕飕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻讨厌那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 应该更深刻意识到自己已经发育…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…虽说一部分没怎么发育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好眼熟的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔好 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 难道是波波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大个 发育期好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 听说利用连接线 互相交换NM就能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 肉好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔我去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我给忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 面麻说过要大家一起才能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 波波 你怎么想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 我也看到幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听可不是看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那只要再得到一个NM的软件…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说谁还有NM…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 我超级讨厌自己的卷毛和眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很羡慕那个拥有飘逸长发的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被仁太喜欢的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣 我们弄一样的贴纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这个可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给安鸣一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最喜欢面麻了 却又很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子 能不能来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊 还要我也玩NM？没门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔回归下童心也没什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们俩好久没过来玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃昨晚鸣子做的果冻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 安鸣的果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 稀有NM是面麻的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 叫你不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…算是她托梦给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻托梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找 NM的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那是「Love&Perry」的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是牛魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 牛魔王啊 是有这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.18,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要找牛魔王 是NM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为面麻在的话 妈妈和安鸣都会变得很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.76,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是DM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.65,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.97,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:00.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.20,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找NM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.36,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NM是吧 对 是NM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.37,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在认真找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.82,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话 你有没有认真找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Bobobo」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种小游戏还写名字 你还真是一板一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔这么久再看「Bobobo」 觉得好好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信 为什么没有魔法宝瓶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为稀有NM不是要交换剧毒怪和元气爆发怪吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野外没有剧毒怪 必须从魔法宝瓶进化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣果然没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很温柔 有很多游戏和漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进化出剧毒怪啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 就当作消磨时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你有回报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学校上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 剩下的就是把连接线插上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这样就可以和朋友交换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请勿中途拔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜！稀有NM友好王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这样面麻也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望 好像不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有好多好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳和安鸣还有波波又变回好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全置身事外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没~事~啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面~麻~最~近~ 遇到的都是开心事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是在(模仿)…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Desu Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最近遇到的都是开心事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久没这么开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我的阴影还没有消失的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有明天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 也可以慢慢找机会道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿~像游戏一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:14.66,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}何ページも費やして 綴られた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:22.06,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}如何してか　一行の空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.13,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}押し花の栞挟んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:30.18,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:37.70,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}忘れかけの煉瓦を積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:42.94,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:50.72,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}怖いくらいに青い空と 右手に咲いた左手は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:55.22,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}ずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:01:02.98,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}そうやって今は僕のほうへ 問い詰めることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:09.87,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}まだ 二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:17.58,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}どうか　また会えますようになんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:25.75,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:14.66,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}用一页又一页 记录下我们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:22.06,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}不知为何 却总是无法填满空白的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.13,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}夹入干花做成的书签
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:30.18,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}和你一同骑上被丢弃的旧单车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:37.70,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}前往那遗忘边缘的碎片砌成的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:42.94,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}跑上可以眺望大海的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:50.72,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}蓝得触目惊心的天空 和右手中探出的左手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:55.22,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}一直在寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:01:02.98,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}如今不必向我追问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:09.87,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}我们明明仍然如此贴近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:17.58,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}却还希望能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:25.75,OP-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}真读不懂自己
